msgctxt "ActivityEditor|"
msgid ""
"If \"Random operands\" is not selected, for each sublevel you must make sure "
"that the \"First operand\" is a multiple of the \"Second operand\"."
msgstr ""
"Ja opcija „Nejaušs operands“ nav atlasīta, jums jāpārliecinās, ka katram "
"apakšlīmenim „Pirmais operands“ ir „Otrā operanda“ dalāmais."

